channel.title: *Deletes Models* *Compiles* *Opens Client* Cache Cannot Be Download!?
channel.description:
Ok, yesterday the following happened:
I was trying to add Staff of Light to my server. It did not work, so I deleted the models. After I compiled and opened client, it said cache cannot be downloaded! I didn't change anything else! I redownloaded the client but the same thing happens. Can anyone help me? I can't work on my server if I can't even login :mad:
